      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a field report for an NGO and need some help with a situational analysis. can u give me a breakdown of the main social tensions in the democratic republic of the congo? specifically, how do the different ethnic groups there interact with each other on a daily basis? i need to understand the landscape before we send the team in.",
